  "title": "Gun Violence: Is Now the Right Time to Talk?  | NYT Opinion",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 1500.0,
      "end_time": 3809.0,
      "text": "Nearly every day, there is a shooting in America."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 3810.0,
      "end_time": 6359.0,
      "text": "But rarely do we consider the impact a shooting has"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 6360.0,
      "end_time": 7560.0,
      "text": "on our elected officials."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 7560.0,
      "end_time": 9809.0,
      "text": "\"I’m more than happy to talk about this in a few days."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 9810.0,
      "end_time": 10940.0,
      "text": "Right now is not the time.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 10940.0,
      "end_time": 13215.0,
      "text": "“There’s a time and place for a political debate.”"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 13215.0,
      "end_time": 15450.0,
      "text": "“But it’s a little bit soon to go into it.”"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 15450.0,
      "end_time": 17160.0,
      "text": "“This is not the time to jump to some conclusion.”"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 17160.0,
      "end_time": 19170.0,
      "text": "“This is not the time to have the discussion.”"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 19170.0,
      "end_time": 22440.0,
      "text": "“Today is not the day.”"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 22440.0,
      "end_time": 25200.0,
      "text": "Introducing Aftershot, the only app"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 25200.0,
      "end_time": 26790.0,
      "text": "that helps a bunch of [expletive] figure out"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 26790.0,
      "end_time": 29400.0,
      "text": "when to talk about gun reform."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 29400.0,
      "end_time": 32250.0,
      "text": "When developing Aftershot, we learned that most politicians"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 32250.0,
      "end_time": 34980.0,
      "text": "actually voted against the C.D.C. researching"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 34980.0,
      "end_time": 38129.0,
      "text": "the scale and scope of our country’s gun crisis."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 38130.0,
      "end_time": 41400.0,
      "text": "Many see that as politicians just not caring about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 41400.0,
      "end_time": 43860.0,
      "text": "But, surely, they care about innocent people being"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 43860.0,
